      "text": "কাম্লাগু মাথাগু",
      "source_page": 428,
      "source_image": "IMG_0428.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "ছাগলগুইন",
      "source_page": 428,
      "source_image": "IMG_0428.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "কামলাগুরো",
      "source_page": 428,
      "source_image": "IMG_0428.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "মনুষ্যবাচক—",
      "source_page": 428,
      "source_image": "IMG_0428.jpg"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "বহুবচন:",
